{"version":1,"entries":{"person_1509675_translations":{"at":1772689421693,"data":{"id":1509675,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Akaso Eiji is a Japanese actor and model, known for playing Ryuga Banjou in Kamen Rider Build. He is currently represented by Tristone Entertainment.\n\nHe belonged to the Nagoya model office \"FORM JAPAN\" when he was in his teens. He was active as a model and talent under the name Mamoru Akaso (赤楚 衛, Akaso Mamoru). In 2010, he joined the local idol group \"BOYS AND MEN\" in Nagoya, working on stage performances and regular appearances of variety shows. Eiji is said to have left \"BOYS AND MEN\" in 2011. Originally, he entered the entertainment agency because he wanted to be an actor and not an idol.\n\nHe won the Grand Prix at the men's model audition of Samantha Thavasa in 2013, which became the turning point for him to audition in Tokyo at the age of 19. The trigger that lead Eiji to drop out of university and to enter the world of entertainment was a call from the CEO of his current agency in 2014. In 2015, he transferred to his current agency Tristone Entertainment, working as an actor and starring in television dramas and films in his current stage name","name":"Eiji Akaso","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"赤楚衛二（日語：赤楚 衛二／あかそ えいじ Akaso Eiji；1994年3月1日－）是日本男演員、模特兒，出身自愛知縣，所屬經紀公司為Tristone娛樂。","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"1994年3月1日出生于日本大阪府守口市，演员、模特。\n\n2010年，加入名古屋男子团体IIKEMENNAGOYA（后BOYS AND MEN），从而进入演艺圈。2015年，出演个人首部电视剧《表参道高校合唱部！》，从而作为演员出道。2016年，出演漫改舞台剧《黑子的篮球 THE ENCOUNTER》。2017年4月7日，其出演的特摄剧《假面骑士Amazons第二季》播出；同年，因出演特摄剧《假面骑士Build》而获得一定的关注。2019年，主演原创特摄影片《Build NEW WORLD 假面骑士Cross-Z》 ；12月5日，其主演的的爱情剧《老师，你不知道吗》播出。2020年，出演悬疑推理剧《美食侦探明智五郎》；8月14日，他参演的漫改校园爱情电影《恋途未卜》上映；10月8日，他主演的漫改爱情剧《到了30岁还是处男，似乎会变成魔法师》播出。","name":"赤楚卫二","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"赤楚衛二","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Eidži Akaso","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ейджі Акасо","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"1994 年 3 月 1 日出生於日本大阪府守口市，演員、模特。\n\n2010 年，加入名古屋男子團體 IIKEMENNAGOYA（後 BOYS AND MEN），從而進入演藝圈。2015 年，出演個人首部電視劇《表參道高校合唱部！》，從而作為演員出道。2016 年，出演漫改舞台劇《黑子的籃球 THE ENCOUNTER》。2017 年 4 月 7 日，其出演的特攝劇《幪面超人 Amazons 第二季》播出；同年，因出演特攝劇《幪面超人 Build》而獲得一定的關注。2019 年，主演原創特攝影片《Build NEW WORLD 幪面超人 Cross - Z》 ；12 月 5 日，其主演的的愛情劇《老師，你不知道嗎》播出。2020 年，出演懸疑推理劇《美食偵探明智五郎》；8 月 14 日，他參演的漫改校園愛情電影《交錯的想念》上映；10 月 8 日，他主演的漫改愛情劇《到了 30 歲還是處男，似乎會變成魔法師》播出。","name":"赤楚衞二","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"아카소 에이지","primary":false}}]}},"person_1939676_translations":{"at":1772689429527,"data":{"id":1939676,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Joseph Andrew Starkey (born November 4, 1993) is an American actor. He began his career with supporting roles in the teen drama films Love, Simon and The Hate U Give (both in 2018). He gained recognition for his portrayal of troubled teenager Rafe Cameron in the Netflix adventure series Outer Banks (2020–present).\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Drew Starkey, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.","name":"Drew Starkey","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"M